    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >5 Brand new Mini Maps!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224670/extras/29cc7488b55b98704bdb8ea661866169.avif?t=1673978097\" width=616 height=352 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >+200 In Game Death Coins</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224670/extras/4452597dcb19675ae2cb37fe505cd316.avif?t=1673978097\" width=167 height=146 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >+5 Awesome Power Ups</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224670/extras/a2eb945eff4b863fb054cc6354693277.avif?t=1673978097\" width=600 height=213 /></span><br><br>Introducing the Mini Maps DLC for our popular multiplayer game!  <br><br><strong>5 Mini Maps (<strong>Mini Beach, Mini Graveyard, Mini Temple, Mini Lab and Mini Western</strong>) | +200 Death Coins | 5 Free Power Ups</strong><br><br>This exciting new addition features five brand new mini maps that are perfect for intense, fast-paced battles.<br><br>First up is <strong>Mini Beach</strong>, where players can fight it out on a sunny sandy beach complete with palm trees and crystal clear waters. Next, we have <strong>Mini Graveyard</strong>, a spooky and atmospheric map set in an old cemetery. For a change of pace, players can head to <strong>Mini Temple</strong>, a beautifully designed temple nestled in a lush jungle.<br><br>For a more futuristic setting, players can check out <strong>Mini Lab</strong>, a high-tech research facility filled with advanced machinery and gadgets. Finally, we have <strong>Mini Western</strong>, a <strong>Wild West</strong>-themed map complete with saloons, sheriffs, and outlaws.<br><br>With these five new mini maps, players can enjoy countless hours of action-packed gameplay in a variety of unique and exciting settings.",
